No. 09-438. Providence Hospital, et al., Petitioners v. Johnella Richmond Moses, Personal Representative of the Estate of Marie Moses-Irons, Deceased. 561 U.S. 1038, 130 S. Ct. 3499,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1113,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5301. June 28, 2010.

Motion of Michigan Health & Hospital Association for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 561 F.3d 573.
